### Login with the created user
POST http://localhost:3000/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "mike.johnson@aurora.com",
    "password": "Plumber2024!"
}

### Get user details (replace TOKEN with the token from login response)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/detail/USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Update user (replace TOKEN and USER_ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/users/USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Test User",
    "phone": "0987654321"
}

### Delete user (replace TOKEN and USER_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

